C94A RunGoomba_entry2
C965 RunKoopa
D295 RunPodoboo
D67A OffscreenBoundsCheck
D680 OffscreenCalcLeftBound
D69A OffscreenCalcRightBound
D6D2 OffscreenDeactivate

# ---- Functions (fixed bank, misc) ----
F152 GetEnemyScreenPosition
F1AF RelativeEnemyPosition
F1B1 RelativeEnemyPosition_entry2
F1BA GetScreenPosition

# ---- Functions (switchable bank) ----
8220 ClearSprites
8245 GameCoreRoutine
